textAnnotations.description:
Looking to buy property?
You're invited to our Home Buying Forum at our Commonwealth Bank London Circuit Branch.
Buying your first property or upgrading to your dream home? Let us show you the easy steps to turn your home ownership dream into a reality.
Come along as we look to provide you all the help and advice you need to buy your home.
Learn how to use the latest banking and finance technology designed specifically to support home buyers
FREE gift bag for all attendees.
We look forward to seeing you there.
When
Thursday 7th December 2017
at 6.00pm
Where
Commonwealth Bank London Circuit
Branch 181 London Circuit, Canberra
RSVP
Please register by phone or email to
Kathy Eliopoulos on 0466 507 713
or Ekaterini. Eliopoulos@cba.com.au
Can
